  <!-- FAQ Section -->
  <section class="faq-section py-16 bg-[#0d0f1a]" style="background: #0d0f1a !important; background-color: #0d0f1a !important;">
    <div class="container max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="section-header text-center mb-10">
        <span class="section-label">FREQUENTLY ASKED QUESTIONS</span>
        <h2 class="section-title">Your SEO <span>Questions Answered</span></h2>
        <p class="section-subtitle">Straight answers on rankings, leads, reporting, AI search, CRO and what happens after you enquire</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="faq-container max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary>How long does SEO take in the Philippines?</summary>
          <p>Most campaigns need 3-6 months before meaningful movement is clear, although technical fixes and page improvements can show earlier signals. The timeline depends on your current site health, competition, authority, content quality and how quickly recommendations are implemented.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary>Do you only work with Philippine businesses?</summary>
          <p>No. We work with Philippine businesses, international companies targeting the Philippines, and agencies that need white-label SEO support. The strategy is scoped around market, language, competition and commercial goals.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary>Can you improve leads without just chasing more traffic?</summary>
          <p>Yes. That is where SEO and CRO meet. We review service pages, CTAs, trust signals, forms, mobile UX, internal links and conversion tracking so the traffic you already have has a better chance of becoming calls, quote requests and enquiries.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary>How do you measure SEO success?</summary>
          <p>We track rankings, GSC clicks and impressions, organic traffic, landing page performance, calls, forms, GBP actions and revenue indicators where available. Rankings matter, but they are only useful when they support commercial growth.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary>Do you help with AI search and Google AI Overviews?</summary>
          <p>Yes, but we keep it grounded in SEO. AI search visibility is built on crawlable pages, clear entities, useful content, proof, authority, schema, reviews and strong service or product information. We do not sell AI ranking shortcuts.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary>What happens after I request an audit?</summary>
          <p>We review your website, rankings, competitors, technical setup and conversion path. Then we identify the highest-impact SEO and CRO opportunities. If there is a fit, we scope a practical roadmap rather than forcing you into a generic package.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary>Do you offer white-label SEO?</summary>
          <p>Yes. We support agencies with confidential white-label SEO delivery, audits, content, technical SEO, reporting and campaign execution. Client communication and branding are agreed before work begins.</p>
        </details>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

